read fort files and apply a name structure

read fort files and apply a name structure

read_fort_factory(basepath, .fort, .names = c("ITERATION", "ID", "TIME", "F",
  "DV", "CL", "V"))

Arguments

basepath

base directory
.fort

fortran file name
.names

column names

Examples

# NOT RUN {
read_fort51 <- read_fort_factory("../modeling", "fort.51")
read_fort51(last_est_dir("run001"))
read_fort51("run001_est_01")
# }
